race.comment: Lots of these struggling to find their best. FIVE STAR KING (2) is fitter for two runs back and with the big claim gets chance. Drawn to be prominent and should give a sight. FORTYFOUR MAGNUM (6) is also ready to fire after two runs in. Extra trip a plus and also aided by the claim. APPPLEBY (7) is overdue for a win, placing last two before a break then placing fresh in a strong return. Fitter and expected to go close. IL CIELO (4) may want a little further down the road but presents fresh on the back of a few hit-outs and has the claim. Expected to be winding up over the top. RICH AND JOYFUL (11) has been mixing form but has the figures to feature and gets chance to atone.
